Z","msg":"自推x12"},{"pid":"95d6ed9957153ca64f1e9a190114333bb01a0a9c","tid":1467633,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6dc61465ee4f979a8d0bb5b12746abab040c999","tid":1467633,"uid":173466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"好簡單，有鬼你又唔知，咁你同隻鬼又唔割，咁你即係同隻鬼一家親。我唔係講點捉鬼，我想講每個人都應該理性思考，要割既係唔理性，有理性就唔可以割，盲講唔割即係幫緊鬼。"},{"pid":"ac6eb08578a034a48488a7907dee17cade7cd0af","tid":1467633,"uid":297071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【突發】許志安回應機場事件</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e69c422e13b1420008460bd69a13a7a605c7b6bf","tid":1467633,"uid":9334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:50.000Z","msg":"推，唔好再打擊自己人士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49aecabf8e8f7515f12ece666eaa568e06a6ec88","tid":1467633,"uid":62210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:55.000Z","msg":"自推x13"},{"pid":"b4406f316cd7bf90d2e95d875c4d929fbf6da8ab","tid":1467633,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:24.000Z","msg":"請手足幫手推<br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 和理飛814<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466833</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a3fe40ba96386a89670c72e2367bfabe5278b8b4","tid":1467633,"uid":62210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"自推x14"},{"pid":"7c91e7c6b99498bae85d73b854f1afd8c7f4f88b","tid":1467633,"uid":62210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6dc61465ee4f979a8d0bb5b12746abab040c999","tid":1467633,"uid":173466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"好簡單，有鬼你又唔知，咁你同隻鬼又唔割，咁你即係同隻鬼一家親。我唔係講點捉鬼，我想講每個人都應該理性思考，要割既係唔理性，有理性就唔可以割，盲講唔割即係幫緊鬼。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"當你無十成把握就唔好亂話人係鬼<br />\n你見到人地又耳機又警員水袋又高大先好去懷疑<br />\n前線手足一定有人比較沖<br />\n但唔好下下都話鬼<br />\n我係人 沖前少少都比人話係鬼<br />\n你覺得我下次重上唔上前線/出黎？<br />\n<br />\n如果懷疑/捉到鬼，唔好對佢和理非<br />\n總之就理性少少！"},{"pid":"52ca4035625da53648b3dc5c1552a0817888fbc5","tid":1467633,"uid":62210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e69c422e13b1420008460bd69a13a7a605c7b6bf","tid":1467633,"uid":9334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:50.000Z","msg":"推，唔好再打擊自己人士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"係！士氣真係好重要！唔好比人打散！"},{"pid":"bb2c3096f10f7f9d721322dcca0c6cc7e83acea7","tid":1467633,"uid":62210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"自推x15"},{"pid":"cc71aa4628ca4bf065d40e8a378fbfcb740d6f64","tid":1467633,"uid":62210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:36.000Z","msg":"自推x16"},{"pid":"aa5b6701eb74a86b183aeec43d0afead0ec745c8","tid":1467633,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"adebbb48866a97b00586a58ab3aaa6a090f505bd","tid":1467633,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8935be74d7726cf1587c920cfac71cf33e09a624","tid":1467633,"uid":286211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:15.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割𥱊 不篤灰"},{"pid":"3132aeabad0b496e9b59a07fb04a2ebdd5e6a0ce","tid":1467633,"uid":62210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:56.000Z","msg":"士氣好重要！唔好比人地/自己打沉！<br />\n我地可以沖！可以錯！但唔好沉！<br />\n錯咗我地可以認錯！<br />\n但士氣一沉就無人打仗！"},{"pid":"406d8ad8785bb087a11ff6416e5b7719cd384bde","tid":1467633,"uid":62210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"